@CodeSmith.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7111

### Create a new session
POST {{CodeSmith.Api_HostAddress}}/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "difficulty": "Easy"
}

### Chat with session (replace sessionId with actual value)
POST {{CodeSmith.Api_HostAddress}}/api/session/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I'm not sure how to approach this problem. Can you give me a hint?"
}
